<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747017>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Aprusia vankhedei n. sp. female from Udawattakele FR. (a) habitus, dorsal view; (b) same, ventral view. The arrow in (b) points to the thick, procurved, sclerotized ridge of the postepigastric scutum. Scale bar = 0.5 mm (a, b)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747017/files/figure.png" .

